make sure you [[Add Plugins in Yabridge for Conversion]] first

``` bash
WINEPREFIX=/path/to/prefix  WINEARCH=win64 yabridge sync
```

fix [["Yabridgectl Status/Sync Prints "Indexed Over 100.000 Files" Yabridge Issue]] if you get it
